flowchart TB
    %% CoreZero Data Stack — 6 layers, highest signal to lowest

    T1["Layer 1 — Router &amp; Entrypoint<br/>AGENTS.md + MASTER_INDEX.md<br/><em>Always loaded</em>"]:::t1
    T2["Layer 2 — Constitution &amp; Policy<br/>core-policies.md · core-zero/rules/ · adr-log.md<br/><em>Always / by-intent</em>"]:::t2
    T3["Layer 3 — Knowledge &amp; Heuristics<br/>project-knowledge-base.md · learned-heuristics.md · core-zero/memories/domain/<br/><em>Loaded on keyword match</em>"]:::t3
    T4["Layer 4 — Feature Artifacts<br/>spec.md · plan.md · tasks.md · review.md · status.md<br/>handoff.md · testing-scenarios.md · session-extracts.md<br/><em>Loaded on active slug</em>"]:::t4
    T5["Layer 5 — Raw Code (JIT)<br/>Source files · generated codemap<br/><em>Just-in-time</em>"]:::t5
    T6["Layer 6 — Transient &amp; Telemetry<br/>Command output · test logs · subagent reports · harness-telemetry.md<br/><em>Session-only / by-debug</em>"]:::t6

    T1 -->|always loaded| T2
    T2 -->|by intent keyword| T3
    T3 -->|on active slug| T4
    T4 -->|read JIT as needed| T5
    T5 -->|run commands/proofs| T6

    T6 -.->|compaction: summarize + evict| T4
    T5 -.->|evict JIT files after task| T4

    LOAD["Load Rules:<br/>Layer 1-2 always · Layer 3 by intent keyword match<br/>Layer 4 on active feature slug · Layer 5 JIT · Layer 6 transient/evicted"]:::note

